    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot add your<strong> salmon fillet[s]</strong>, skin-side down, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 9-10 min, turning once halfway, or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 2,
