    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 25g <span class=\"text-purple\">[35g]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [50g]</span> <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once melted, add your <strong>gnocchi</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to brown slightly</p>",
